Hollywood plus / DXR3 device driver for Linux

For further information, visit the webpage at http://dxr3.sourceforge.net/

Things are currently being autoconfed.  The kernel modules still need to
be built separately.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a WIP rework to get the driver running on kernels 5.x and 6.x.

It is so far not tested properly.

